<h2>Game Rules</h2>

<h3><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag">&nbsp;</span>Changes</h3>

<p>You can make a maximum of three changes to your team between races.</p>

<h3><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag">&nbsp;</span>Race Entry Deadline</h3>

<p>Your team selection will be locked from Fri 8pm before a race weekend.</p>

